  "detector_aggregation_description": "At each timestamp, compute the per-sensor Gaussian log-likelihood ratio llr_{i,t} = ((x_{i,t} - mu_{0,i})^2 - (x_{i,t} - mu_{1,i})^2) / (2 sigma_i^2) using fixed global empirical parameters, then average across active sensors with finite readings. Apply the one-sided CUSUM S_t = max(0, S_{t-1} + L_t) and detect when S_t >= h.",
  "detector_parameters": {
    "evidence_type": "gaussian_log_likelihood_ratio",
    "formula": "llr_{i,t} = ((x_{i,t} - mu_{0,i})^2 - (x_{i,t} - mu_{1,i})^2) / (2 sigma_i^2); L_t = mean_{i in S_t} llr_{i,t}; S_t = max(0, S_{t-1} + L_t); detect when S_t >= h."
  },
